bib.title: Search For Quartet Excited States In 16O

free_txt: SD
VS. The unit code for the incident energy
in suben. 014 MEV -> KEV.
Alphas, protons and the elastic deuterons were
separated either by coincidence-anticoincidence
technique or by two-parameter analysis of dE and E
signals. The transmission detectors were taken 14 mu-m
to 55 mu-m thick, according to the kinematics.
Digitizing error
The errors of the cross-sections were
calculated on the basis of the standard deviations of
counting rates as determined by the least-square fits
and normalization errors and are indicated by bars for
typical cases in the figures.
Melamine targets (C2H6N4) evaporated onto 20 mu-g/cm2
carbon backings were used. A thin Au layer prevented
the melamine from evaporating during bombardment.
